%% Diagram: Active-passive failover sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Mon as Monitor
    participant DNS as Global DNS / LB
    participant Pri as Primary region
    participant Std as Standby region
    participant App as App services (standby)

    Mon->>Pri: Health checks fail (timeout / 5xx)
    Mon->>Mon: Confirm beyond suppression threshold
    Mon->>Pri: Fence (revoke writes, stop replication)
    Mon->>Std: Promote standby DB to primary
    Std-->>Mon: Promotion complete (new write endpoint)
    Mon->>App: Scale up to production capacity
    App-->>Mon: Ready (warm caches, dependencies healthy)
    Mon->>DNS: Repoint write traffic to standby region
    DNS-->>App: Production traffic begins
    App->>App: Smoke / synthetic checks pass
    Mon-->>Mon: Declare recovery complete (RTO clock stops)
